data.description: Don't wait for new construction!  Take a look at this beautiful single-family home built in 2021, located in the desirable gated community of  PARKVIEW AT LONG LAKE RANCH. This community has it all, playgrounds for the little ones, a dog park and  an amazing resort style pool for everyone to enjoy. This home features 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms, 2 car garage, PLUS a flex room or DEN which can easily be the 4th bedroom. Vaulted ceilings, recess lights, open concept. The kitchen has a gorgeous backsplash, 42" soft close cabinets, stainless steel appliances, a nice pantry with plenty of space, beautiful granite countertops, and a large island. The living room is spacious and open with 3 panel sliding patio doors in the back. The bedrooms are nice and very spacious, walk-in shower in the owner's suite, dual vanity, separate toilet and there two closets.  The garage was updated with epoxy floors, there is sprinkler system around the house, large washer/dryer included, the backyard is completely fenced in, St. Augustin green grass around the house, a lot of space for children to play. Solar panels were installed in 2022, do not hesitate and schedule your private showing today.
